data.title: Jimi Hendrix
data.meta_description: Guitarist and songwriter.  Born Washington, USA. View from the Mirror has done a wonderful job plotting Hendrix's London, with lots of pictures including ones we had not seen before taken on the day of his death.  Died at the Hotel Samarkand, 22 Lansdowne Crescent, from a drug and alcohol overdose.  See Londonist for more on Hendrix's life in London.
data.text:
Guitarist and songwriter. Born Washington, USA. View from the Mirror has done a wonderful job plotting Hendrix's London, with lots of pictures including ones we had not seen before taken on the day of his death. Died at the Hotel Samarkand, 22 Lansdowne Crescent, from a drug and alcohol overdose.

See Londonist for more on Hendrix's life in London.
